data.description: Welcome to this stunning WATERFRONT POOL home on almost HALF AN ACRE with a BRAND NEW ROOF. This beautiful property offers privacy and tranquility, with the added bonus of a backyard pond where you can catch bass! The outdoor space features a garden area, fruit trees, an arrangement of plants and flowers, a chicken coop, 10x16 shed and a fire pit, perfect for cozy evenings under the stars.     Enter through the large screened in front porch and inside you’ll find three bedrooms and a den including a spacious master bedroom with dual closets and french doors that open to the lanai and pool area. The master bathroom boasts a luxurious walkthrough shower. The private master bedroom sits on one side of the home while the 2 bedrooms and den are on the opposite side and can even be closed off with a pocket door for added privacy. These rooms share the second bathroom which also conveniently serves as a pool bath. The living room, family room, and formal dining room all feature cathedral ceilings and provide ample space for relaxation and entertaining. The large kitchen can accommodate a small table for a breakfast area looking out to the pool and back yard.     This home is equipped with several convenient amenities such as an indoor laundry room with a sink, central vacuum system, and an intercom system throughout the house. For entertainment enthusiasts, the property is wired for sound with a full theater system and for added security and peace of mind, the home is equipped with a security system and cameras.  Other notable features include Manabloc plumbing and an automated sprinkler system.    Enjoy your days in the back lanai and pool with plenty of space for entertaining. Parking will never be an issue with the three-car garage and oversized driveway, providing plenty of space for your vehicles and toys.    Recent updates include a brand new roof in 2023, exterior painting 2022, the replacement of the top half of the pool screens in 2023 and the lower half in 2021, pumping of the aerobic septic tank 2023, and servicing of the 2019 air conditioner in May 2023. The property also features a new oven and a reverse osmosis system under the kitchen sink for drinking water.    Located in Tropical Gulf Acres with NO deed restrictions, this waterfront pool home won’t last long. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a piece of paradise!
